com.qbpsimulator.engine.model.xsd

Class DistributionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qbpsimulator.engine.model.xsd.DistributionInfo

  • public class DistributionInfo
extends Object
    Distribution info type is used to define durations of elements following given distributions. All values are in seconds.

    Java class for DistributionInfo complex type.
